  <p>This is an educational breakdown of tirzepatide, covering its mechanisms, clinical trial data, dosing protocols, side effects, and comparison to semaglutide. It is <strong>not a recommendation to use tirzepatide</strong>. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting any medication.</p>
