<p>For a deeper compound profile, visit <a href="https://peptidearc.com">PeptideArc</a>.</p>

<!-- ========== MECHANISMS ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>How Tirzepatide Works: Dual Incretin Agonism</h2>

<p>Both GLP-1 and GIP are <strong>incretin hormones</strong> released by your gut after eating. They regulate insulin, appetite, and energy balance. Tirzepatide mimics both of them at the same time.</p>

